---
// Contact.astro
---

<section id="contact" class="relative py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-900/20 via-black to-black"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-red-600/20 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-20"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black font-plus-jakarta mb-8">
      お問い合わせ<span class="text-red-500">.</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      IT課題解決、HP制作、自動化のご相談はお気軽にメールをください。<br />
      24時間以内にご返信いたします。
    </p>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-950 border border-red-600/30 rounded-2xl p-12 hover:border-red-600/60 transition-colors">
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">メールで直接お問い合わせ：</p>
      <a href="mailto:r.takeuchi@tech-i.net" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 hover:from-red-500 hover:to-red-600 text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-red-500/50">
        r.takeuchi@tech-i.net
      </a>
      <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <p>
          GitHub:
          <a href="https://github.com/TECH-i-main" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-gray-200">
            https://github.com/TECH-i-main
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>